rows.label: qst702407_msg0001
rows.name:
*Yawn*... Guarding a
warehouse is so boring...

rows.label: qst702407_msg0002
rows.name:
But I don't like being busy either,
so maybe this is for the best...

rows.label: qst702407_msg0003
rows.name: Huh? You have the perfect job for me?

rows.label: qst702407_msg0004
rows.name:
If I join the resistance, I
get three meals a day and a
nap, except in emergencies?

rows.label: qst702407_msg0005
rows.name:
No way... I may not look
it, but I'm a brave soldier
of the Iiran army.

rows.label: qst702407_msg0006
rows.name:
Even if the resistance is
under Adel-sama's command, I
can't just leave so easily.

rows.label: qst702407_msg0007
rows.name:
...But if that's true, I
might be a little tempted...

rows.label: qst702407_msg0008
rows.name:
If I feel like it, I'll go
to the resistance camp, so
could you wait a bit?

rows.label: qst702407_msg0102
rows.name:
Should I join the resistance and slack
off...? Or should I stay here and slack
off in front of the warehouse...?

rows.label: qst702407_msg0103
rows.name:
Huh? Wait a minute, aren't those
two pretty much the same thing?
